data.name: grdPaCnt.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT A.GWA GWA , FN_BAS_LOAD_GWA_NAME(A.GWA, A.NAEWON_DATE) GWA_NAME , FN_BAS_LOAD_DOCTOR_NAME(A.DOCTOR, A.NAEWON_DATE) DOCTOR_NAME , COUNT(1) PA_CNT FROM OUT1001 A , BAS0102 B WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.NAEWON_DATE = :f_naewon_date AND NVL(A.NAEWON_YN, 'N') <> 'N' AND NVL(A.NAEWON_YN, 'N') <> 'E' AND A.JUBSU_GUBUN = B.CODE AND B.CODE_TYPE = 'JUBSU_GUBUN' AND B.GROUP_KEY IN ('1','2') GROUP BY A.NAEWON_DATE, A.GWA, A.DOCTOR ORDER BY substr(A.DOCTOR,3) ,A.GWA, A.DOCTOR
